13 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1151.18, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 1151.18. Upon request, the registrar shall verify a
16 roofing contractor registration number to city, county and state
17 enforcement officials and to the public. The registrar shall
18 establish through the Internet or other technology a verification
19 system or direct access system for confirming roofing contractor
20 registration certificates and status of registration maintained by
21 the Construction Industries Board. The system shall include the
22 notation of each complaint received against an individual roofing
23 contractor, his or her response to each complaint by noting whether
24 the roofing contractor admits or denies the allegation, any court
